@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.cos((v0 + 0.35 - tmp + 0.26)))
    v1 = (0.90 + (0.67 + tmp))
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.cos(v0 + 0.34) + wp.sin(tmp + 0.49)))
    tmp = (0.84 * ((v2 + 0.74 / v1 + 0.00) + (v0 + 0.92 - v1 + 0.58)))
    data[tid] = v0
